name: $location
desc: Returns: The location where the encounter takes place.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The location where the encounter takes place.

name: $status
desc: Returns: The status of the participants' presence at the specified location during the period specified. If the participant is no longer at the location, then the period will have an end date/time.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The status of the participants' presence at the specified location during the period specified. If the participant is no longer at the location, then the period will have an end date/time.

name: $physicalType
desc: Returns: This will be used to specify the required levels (bed/ward/room/etc.) desired to be recorded to simplify either messaging or query.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: This will be used to specify the required levels (bed/ward/room/etc.) desired to be recorded to simplify either messaging or query.

name: $period
desc: Returns: Time period during which the patient was present at the location.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Time period during which the patient was present at the location.
